1. A CRM Analytics dashboard is:
Solution : B. A multi-faceted view of your data 

2. An app's navigation panel shows:
Solution : C. A list of the dashboards and lenses in the app

3. You can filter a CRM Analytics dashboard by:
Solution : D. Both A and C

4. Drill down into a dashboard widget by:
Solution : C. Selecting Explore from the widget's dropdown menu, clicking a segment on the chart, and then right-clicking the segment
